To better point out the totally unphysical character of the quantum-kinetic results in Figs.~\ref{Fig3} and \ref{Fig4}, we can perform an exact numerical solution of the electron-plus-one phonon system just considered. More specifically, by denoting with $\hat{{\boldsymbol{\rho}}}$ the global (electron-plus-phonon) density-matrix operator, its time evolution can be expressed as

text:
\begin{equation}\label{EE}
\frac{d\hat{{\boldsymbol{\rho}}}}{dt}
=
\frac{1}{\imath\hbar}\,\left[\hat H, \hat{{\boldsymbol{\rho}}}\right]
+
\Gamma_{\rm p}
\left(
\hat b^{ }_{\overline{\mathbf{q}}}
\hat{{\boldsymbol{\rho}}}
\hat b^\dagger_{\overline{\mathbf{q}}}
-
\frac{1}{2} 
\left\{
\hat b^\dagger_{\overline{\mathbf{q}}}
\hat b^{ }_{\overline{\mathbf{q}}}
,
\hat{{\boldsymbol{\rho}}}
\right\}\right)\ ,
\end{equation}
